General.Name: Advanced SolTech Sweden AB
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Advanced Soltech Sweden AB (publ) engages in the financing, installing, owning, and managing solar PV installations in China and Sweden. The company serves medium-sized and large private public companies, state-owned companies, and organisations. Advanced Soltech Sweden AB (publ) was founded in 2014 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
